Orzag Sees Restructuring of Greek Debt This Year

-- B y  
-- 
2011-10-12T16:06:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/orzag-sees-restructuring-of-greek-debt-this-year-video-.html
Peter Orszag, vice chairman of 
global banking at Citigroup Inc. and a former director of the 
Office of Management and Budget, talks about the European 
sovereign-debt crisis and its likely impact on the U.S.  Orzag, speaking on Bloomberg Television's "InBusiness with 
Margaret Brennan," also discusses yesterday's 
Bloomberg/Washington Post Republican presidential debate about 
the economy. (Orszag is a Bloomberg View columnist. The 
opinions expressed are his own. Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 07:12
 